action.content:
You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: London
TO: Lyon
BY: Boat
CLASS: The cheapest
WHEN: In two weeks

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <some text>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <some text>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  Have you already mentioned the origin of your trip to the travel agent? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Have you already mentioned the origin of your trip to the travel agent? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: No, I haven't mentioned the origin of my trip to the travel agent yet.
Answer for FROM valid after 2 tries.
ME:  Does the travel agent already know your destination? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Does the travel agent already know your destination? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: No, the travel agent does not know my destination yet.
Answer for TO valid after 2 tries.
ME:  Do you believe that the travel agent is aware of how you are going to travel? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: No, the travel agent is not aware of my travel plans yet.
Answer for BY valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Is the travel agent aware of which class you would like to book? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Is the travel agent aware of which class you would like to book? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: The customer wants to book the cheapest class for their travel from London to Lyon by boat in two weeks. The travel agent is not aware of this yet.
ME: Please follow my instructions. Is the travel agent aware of which class you would like to book? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please be specific now. Is the travel agent aware of which class you would like to book? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please think about it carefully. Is the travel agent aware of which class you would like to book? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: The customer wants to book the cheapest class for their travel from London to Lyon by boat in two weeks. The travel agent is not aware of these details yet.
Answer for CLASS invalid after max attempts.
ME:  Do you think the travel agent knows when you want to leave? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: No, the travel agent does not know when I want to leave yet.
Answer for WHEN valid after 1 tries.
